data.value:
Select a map on the left you'd like to load. Hit "Launch Halo Online" When you get to the main menu, hit "DarkLoad."
Enjoy!
This DarkLoader is for Eldorado.exe Version 0.4.1.4409, but it might work for newer\older builds.... Pattern Scanning rocks!
